    "content": "<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"width: 100.0%; border-collapse: collapse;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 15.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 12.2%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 15.0pt;\" width=\"12%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;\"><br /></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">一级类目</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 12.26%; border-top: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-left: none; background: #c00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; height: 15pt; line-height: 2;\" width=\"12%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">二级类目</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 24.18%; border-top: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-left: none; background: #c00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; height: 15pt; line-height: 2;\" width=\"24%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">行业资质</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 48.68%; border-top: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid black; background: #c00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; height: 15pt; line-height: 2;\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"48%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">特殊资质及要求</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 2;\" width=\"2%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 15pt; border: none; line-height: 2;\" width=\"0\" height=\"30\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 18.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 12.2%; border-top: none; border-left: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 18.5pt;\" rowspan=\"19\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"12%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">生鲜</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 12.26%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 18.5pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"12%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">水果</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 24.18%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 18.5pt;\" rowspan=\"2\" width=\"24%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">/</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 24.42%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 18.5pt;\" rowspan=\"2\" width=\"24%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">/</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 24.26%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 18.5pt;\" rowspan=\"19\" width=\"24%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1. </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">商家若销售的新鲜水果、蔬菜和鲜蛋未注册品牌，可不提供商标注册证或商标注册申请受理通知书图片，在系统中选择&rdquo;无品牌&ldquo;选项即可。<br /><br />2. 报关单和入境货物检验检疫证明（经营进口商品）：需提供近一年内的中华人民共和国进口货物报关单以及近一年内的同批次（以合同号进行判断）商品的入境货物检验检疫证明或出入境检验检疫卫生证书图片，报关单上应展现对应品牌名称及商品名称，卫检证明如有附页需提供完整。若商家非报关单上的经营单位或收货单位，则需提供以报关单上的经营单位或收货单位为源头的完整授权链路文件图片，或者提供商家近三个月内向上一级经销商进货的发票图片。</span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: none; padding: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm;\" width=\"2%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 18.5pt; border: none;\" width=\"0\" height=\"37\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 18.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 12.26%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 18.5pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"12%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">蔬菜</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: none; padding: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm;\" width=\"2%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 18.5pt; border: none;\" width=\"0\" height=\"37\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 37.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 12.26%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 37.0pt;\" rowspan=\"9\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"12%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">海鲜水产</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 24.18%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 37.0pt;\" rowspan=\"17\" width=\"24%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">若经营预包装食品，还需提供以下资质：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><br />1. </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">入驻开店公司的《食品经营许可证》，若当地销售预包装食品仅需备案，请上传备案回执；若当地销售预包装食品备案工作未开展，可提供情况说明。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><br />2. </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">若入驻开店公司是生产商，且经营的产品全部为入驻商生产的产品可提交《食品生产许可证》代替《食品经营许可证》。</span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 24.42%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 37.0pt;\" rowspan=\"9\" width=\"24%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1. </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">经营活蟹产品（包括大闸蟹、青蟹等），必须提交水域养殖租赁合同（包括不限于进货/采购证明、授权书、水域滩涂养殖证），若经营阳澄湖大闸蟹还需提供：<br />① 农产品地理标志登记证书；<br />② 阳澄湖大闸蟹地理标志使用协议；<br />③ 苏州市阳澄湖大闸蟹行业协会给予的授权书。</span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: none; padding: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm;\" width=\"2%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 37.0pt; border: none;\" width=\"0\" height=\"74\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 37.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 2.68%; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 37.0pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"2%\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"height: 37.0pt; border: none;\" width=\"0\" height=\"74\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 37.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 2.68%; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 37.0pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"2%\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"height: 37.0pt; border: none;\" width=\"0\" height=\"74\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 37.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 2.68%; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 37.0pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"2%\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"height: 37.0pt; border: none;\" width=\"0\" height=\"74\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 37.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 2.68%; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 37.0pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"2%\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"height: 37.0pt; border: none;\" width=\"0\" height=\"74\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 37.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 2.68%; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 37.0pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"2%\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"height: 37.0pt; border: none;\" width=\"0\" height=\"74\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 37.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 2.68%; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 37.0pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"2%\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"height: 37.0pt; border: none;\" width=\"0\" height=\"74\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 37.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 2.68%; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 37.0pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"2%\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"height: 37.0pt; border: none;\" width=\"0\" height=\"74\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 37.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 2.68%; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 37.0pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"2%\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"height: 37.0pt; border: none;\" width=\"0\" height=\"74\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 204.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 12.26%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 204.5pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"12%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">生鲜卡券</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 24.42%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 204.5pt;\" width=\"24%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">经营卡券，必须提交：<br />1. 礼券发行方及授权供应商的营业执照经营范围中必须有对应品类项；<br />2. 必须提交发卡方的预付卡备案证明（当地取消可提供取消证明）；<br />3. 入驻商非发卡方，发卡企业向备案机关提交的包含该入驻商家（售卡单位）的售卡企业清单及承诺函（入驻商家为发卡方无需提供此项），模板链接：链接地：</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://3.cn/10g-P44xc\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">https://3.cn/1